Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.36,0:00:32.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,开始得了吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.65,0:00:35.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别一脸沉着地说出这么令人绝望的话！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.89,0:00:38.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪会死…怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.11,0:00:41.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在就绝望还为时过早
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.20,0:00:43.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,先确认一点
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.91,0:00:44.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,功
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.88,0:00:45.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.91,0:00:51.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你说过巴迪失去了平时的冷静呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.29,0:00:53.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.60,0:00:57.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,问她也不好好回答
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.94,0:01:01.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 逃犯中的一员是原伊兹…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.31,0:01:03.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,伊兹达…什么的？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.77,0:01:04.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,伊兹达鲁塔？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.23,0:01:06.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对对  就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.73,0:01:11.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,自从知道了这点后她就变得奇怪起来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.34,0:01:15.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然后你就梦见了白奥林
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.04,0:01:18.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,伊兹达鲁塔和白奥林有关吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.91,0:01:21.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是幻觉重现效果呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.91,0:01:21.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs18\pos(351,364)}flashback
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.85,0:01:25.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原生意识陷入了收缩状态
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.85,0:01:25.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs18\pos(277,364)}original mind
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.06,0:01:28.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和多雷医生预想的一样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.04,0:01:31.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你们说的我完全不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.43,0:01:32.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,千川功
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.56,0:01:35.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来希望你能进行一次旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.49,0:01:37.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,旅行？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.85,0:01:39.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都这时候还开玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.02,0:01:42.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,目的地是巴迪的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.59,0:01:43.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.99,0:01:50.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪的意识正在陷入她自身的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.96,0:01:53.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你能进入她自己断片
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.10,0:01:57.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,正是因为作为过滤器的她  意识的机能已经停止的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.10,0:01:57.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs18\pos(260,364)}filter
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.04,0:02:00.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你在其中再次体验她的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.04,0:02:02.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明智地做出对应
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.33,0:02:06.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就能阻止混乱蔓延
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.65,0:02:11.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这么做巴迪就能回来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.86,0:02:15.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,至少可以阻止人格的消失
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.72,0:02:22.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,总之  这是避免进一步精神融合的唯一对策
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.38,0:04:05.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,使用调整槽进行精神潜行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.38,0:04:05.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs18\pos(429,364)}mind dive
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.24,0:04:07.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,组件启动
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.53,0:04:09.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs20}System idling start{\r}\N系统空载启动
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.18,0:04:21.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我进入巴迪的记忆 会不会造成进一步的混乱…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.15,0:04:23.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.78,0:04:26.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,即使在潜行中也会保持你的意识独立
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.11,0:04:29.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,渗透液程序已经调整过了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.03,0:04:35.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你的意识  包括你之后的体验都会显示出来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.18,0:04:38.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,潜行中也可以进行通信
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.56,0:04:40.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,万一出现危险
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.76,0:04:42.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就会立刻让你醒来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.33,0:04:54.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可能你会看到比梦中更加凄惨的光景
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.79,0:04:57.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.97,0:04:59.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会一直注视着你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.45,0:05:02.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,千万不要慌张
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.03,0:05:07.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.33,0:05:09.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪  早上了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.96,0:05:10.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快起来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.31,0:05:20.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好  白奥林
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.91,0:05:23.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好  巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.22,0:05:26.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的早饭呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.67,0:05:28.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很快就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.61,0:05:31.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,先去洗个澡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.72,0:05:32.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.34,0:05:36.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs20}切  知道我是马格罗马鲁还敢撒野
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.99,0:05:37.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.14,0:05:41.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你现在巴迪10岁左右的记忆里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.85,0:05:45.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然感觉像是在做梦  但马上就会习惯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.28,0:05:48.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此  这个人就是白奥林
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.31,0:05:51.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  不是人吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.40,0:05:56.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}距阿克拉巴鲁外苑行政区恐怖事件已经快2年了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.48,0:06:01.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}中心塔内正在为追悼仪式做准备
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.93,0:06:07.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}另外  现在还未能掌握首犯克丽丝蒂{\fn方正黑体_GBK}菈{\r}·利比的行踪…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.66,0:06:11.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不快点会迟到哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.40,0:06:13.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.89,0:06:17.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,忘记了吗  你从今天起…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.19,0:06:20.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.82,0:06:39.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为大家介绍新朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.11,0:06:41.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是巴迪·希冯·阿鲁提拉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.50,0:06:43.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请大家多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.30,0:06:55.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,奥里奥特拉幼年学校欢迎你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.46,0:06:58.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那入座吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.55,0:07:00.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在最后面  米勒的边上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.68,0:07:03.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么开始上课
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.23,0:07:05.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,打开课本52页
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.19,0:07:10.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,关于帝国最后一百年间的内乱…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.86,0:07:12.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你那滑板算什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.96,0:07:14.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.26,0:07:19.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别坐这东西  靠自己的脚走怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.58,0:07:21.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你是野蛮人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.70,0:07:23.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.55,0:07:32.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,会中这么简单的招  你真是个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.62,0:07:34.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吶  你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.75,0:07:37.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果想说什么的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.94,0:07:40.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.25,0:07:42.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,阿留多人在撒野
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.79,0:07:43.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,克雷德被欺负了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.13,0:07:44.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.28,0:07:46.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,野蛮人！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.53,0:07:52.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,第一天就这样  今后可真令人担心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.37,0:07:54.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,麦基乌斯先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.93,0:07:59.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为身分担保人是你  我才答应她入学的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.85,0:08:01.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  校长…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.34,0:08:03.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我才没有使用暴力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.72,0:08:08.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你没那意思  对普通学生来说可不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.14,0:08:12.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为阿克拉巴鲁恐怖事件的追悼仪式等事情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.76,0:08:16.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都在警惕着阿留多人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.66,0:08:18.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说是时期不对
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.76,0:08:23.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但还希望你们加强监督  不要再次出现轻率的举动
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.56,0:08:25.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怖事件的追悼…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.47,0:08:29.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看到还不是单纯的欺负新学生呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.90,0:08:30.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.16,0:08:33.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不会因为是阿留多人就遭到歧视
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.38,0:08:40.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是因为你让她去学校
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.10,0:08:42.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,出现了  蜥蜴大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.21,0:08:46.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是为了让这孩子了解真正的社会
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.85,0:08:49.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哼  现场需要地方是这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.01,0:08:52.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪  今天起会加大难度
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.54,0:08:53.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能跟上来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.89,0:08:55.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是  斯凯尔兹奥教官
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.29,0:08:58.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那  麦基乌斯警部补  一会再见
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.22,0:09:06.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的对手是程度强化后的西昂Ⅱ型10台
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.71,0:09:08.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小看它们的话  可是会吃苦头的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.24,0:09:09.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,帝托
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.95,0:09:12.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,帝托！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.37,0:09:16.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和平常一样记录数据  不许插嘴哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.82,0:09:17.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.70,0:09:19.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你好  帝托
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.30,0:09:21.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天也麻烦了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.97,0:09:23.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,彼此彼此  巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.77,0:09:24.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.55,0:09:29.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,模拟战  训练开始！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.19,0:09:42.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是训练？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.90,0:09:45.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  麦基乌斯先生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.64,0:09:46.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.66,0:09:51.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,联邦警察进修生的实战训练
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.73,0:09:53.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,进修生的训练？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.03,0:09:58.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪她小时候开始就想当联邦搜查官吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.99,0:10:00.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,并不是想当
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.18,0:10:03.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是注定要当
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.66,0:10:05.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为她是「依古西奥拉」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.07,0:10:07.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「依古西奥拉」…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.89,0:10:14.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,依古西奥拉是从古代技术中诞生阿留多人优性种
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.62,0:10:18.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他们因为被施于调整
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.42,0:10:23.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,拥有强韧的肉体和超越常人的各种能力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.42,0:10:27.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的能力当然不能浪费
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.13,0:10:30.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因此从小就在管理之下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.73,0:10:32.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,警察或者与军队相关
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.62,0:10:35.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,职业也早已注定
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.52,0:10:41.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪连自己的未来也不能选择吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.11,0:10:45.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是…「依古西奥拉」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.03,0:11:49.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.38,0:11:56.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还能撑多久呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.15,0:11:59.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛痛痛痛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.01,0:12:03.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  是不是太用力了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.63,0:12:04.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.16,0:12:07.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然很痛但是感觉很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.82,0:12:11.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,接受斯凯尔兹奥教官的特训后得好好治疗才行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.42,0:12:14.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.94,0:12:18.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,依古西奥拉只能过注定的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.47,0:12:20.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只是被制造出来的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.48,0:12:24.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪是这样出生的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.37,0:12:29.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到此为止！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.46,0:12:32.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,更新了最短记录
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.15,0:12:37.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,完成任务的所用时间  10048
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.95,0:12:43.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,肉体损害  比上回有所下降
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.41,0:12:45.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.48,0:12:49.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你的天分真好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.29,0:12:54.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是一定要注意不能对一般市民使用这份力量
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.57,0:12:59.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,会被当成怪物为世间所忌讳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.83,0:13:00.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.05,0:13:02.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,先前在学校…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.62,0:13:03.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不管学校！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.09,0:13:06.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,麦基乌斯被骂两句就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.99,0:13:07.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.99,0:13:11.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,来  吃好东西去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.41,0:13:12.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我说你啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.73,0:13:21.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,阿留多人怎么能在这里恬不知耻地走着
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.71,0:13:23.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这小鬼真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.76,0:13:26.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是你们先撞我的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.65,0:13:27.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.84,0:13:30.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是个阿留多人  这小鬼还真狂妄
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.56,0:13:32.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是臭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.63,0:13:33.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,阿留多人！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.81,0:13:46.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这小鬼也算是阿留多人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.26,0:13:50.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙也可能是杀人不眨眼的恐怖分子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.02,0:13:51.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.88,0:13:57.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个阿留多人小鬼怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.27,0:14:00.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是依…依古西奥拉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.30,0:14:01.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,依…！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.34,0:14:03.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大人不应该打小孩！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.89,0:14:11.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为对手是怪物！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.92,0:14:13.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可不想扯上关系
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.26,0:14:16.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  你流了好多血呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.26,0:14:18.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,依古西奥拉？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.85,0:14:22.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不太明白  不过面对乌鲁卡人或卡鲁贝兰托人也不会输
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.29,0:14:24.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.82,0:14:25.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,痛…！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.48,0:14:26.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.23,0:14:27.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,血止住前要忍耐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.19,0:14:30.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  我叫巴迪  你呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.84,0:14:32.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那塔鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.04,0:14:34.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那塔鲁？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.40,0:14:35.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看来你知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.87,0:14:37.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个人现在就在地球
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.18,0:14:39.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.54,0:14:40.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…不…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.76,0:14:41.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.80,0:14:44.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不知道这话该不该说…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.22,0:14:47.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个人的父亲原来是伊兹达鲁塔成员
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.80,0:14:50.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,并且协助了逃犯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.54,0:14:51.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.56,0:14:54.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  到我家去吧  就在这附近
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.36,0:14:57.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,让白奥林帮你治疗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.45,0:14:59.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,白奥林？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.56,0:15:00.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对  快点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.10,0:15:04.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.51,0:15:12.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,白奥林  材料放在这里咯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.25,0:15:14.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢  巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.38,0:15:16.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你在放学的路上？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.81,0:15:19.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有上学
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.72,0:15:23.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么？  去上学吧  很有趣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.13,0:15:26.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你明明每天回来都在抱怨
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.92,0:15:29.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经和克雷德与米勒成为好朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.24,0:15:33.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然刚开始被欺负过  但现在关系很好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.64,0:15:35.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了  巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.07,0:15:38.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天又交到一个朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.40,0:15:40.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对对  那塔鲁是好朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.88,0:15:43.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那塔鲁  来吃可提吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.37,0:15:46.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧  白奥林做的可提可好吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.87,0:15:48.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,马上就好了  等一下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.51,0:15:51.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.03,0:16:03.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪  慢慢吃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.04,0:16:06.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那塔鲁吓了一跳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.42,0:16:08.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为很好吃嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.30,0:16:10.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,来  那塔鲁也吃嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.83,0:16:11.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.22,0:16:14.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.37,0:16:18.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不用那么客气
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.87,0:16:23.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,多吃点哦  那塔鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.58,0:16:25.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.03,0:16:39.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再见  巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.34,0:16:40.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.50,0:16:41.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.24,0:16:52.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  那塔鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.52,0:16:56.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有时间吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.67,0:17:04.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那塔鲁的爸爸？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.52,0:17:07.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  让我带你来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.95,0:17:14.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌吗  这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.05,0:17:19.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吶  他们在干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.08,0:17:21.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,纸牌游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.33,0:17:22.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.53,0:17:23.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,星惠果
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.58,0:17:24.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.92,0:17:25.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我家公寓
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.39,0:17:27.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.49,0:17:28.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,楼梯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.39,0:17:29.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.54,0:17:30.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.50,0:17:31.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.75,0:17:33.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.43,0:17:36.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是这么玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.49,0:17:39.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.10,0:17:41.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.56,0:17:42.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,丘乐酷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.66,0:17:44.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸做的小孩玩具
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.60,0:17:50.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.08,0:17:54.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.62,0:17:59.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎回来  真早呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.26,0:18:02.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这个男人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.56,0:18:05.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  他就是那塔鲁的爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.02,0:18:09.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…我叫巴迪·希冯  你好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.08,0:18:13.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,希冯？ 果然是依古西奥拉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.08,0:18:13.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs20}（希冯：联邦学术研究行星希冯。巴迪·希冯·阿鲁提拉的\N真正含义就是「从希冯中诞生的阿留多人」）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.56,0:18:14.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道吗  爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.42,0:18:19.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,昨日犬子受你照顾了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.29,0:18:21.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我并没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.75,0:18:24.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧  一起吃个饭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.07,0:18:30.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哇  终于来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.76,0:18:32.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真晚啊  塔斯克
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.98,0:18:34.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已经完成了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.59,0:18:37.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没工作了正好有时间
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.73,0:18:39.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你这付得起钱的家伙终于来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.91,0:18:42.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,运河的工程完成后我也该失业了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.79,0:18:44.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很可爱的小妹妹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.85,0:18:46.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那塔鲁的女朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.51,0:18:51.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,年纪小小技术一流啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.31,0:18:58.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是她从乌鲁卡人手上救了犬子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.04,0:19:01.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个女该吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.82,0:19:02.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,从乌鲁卡人手中？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.41,0:19:05.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她是依古西奥拉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.55,0:19:06.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,依…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.47,0:19:07.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,依古西奥拉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.22,0:19:11.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  在这里没关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.54,0:19:14.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对对  反正是贫民窟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.92,0:19:16.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,过来吧  小美女
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.36,0:19:17.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,来来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.15,0:19:20.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你在干什么呢  那塔鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.99,0:19:23.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快给小美女带路啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.61,0:19:27.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没错没错  男人就应该陪伴着女孩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.57,0:19:29.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.99,0:19:32.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你在干什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.77,0:19:36.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就算同样是阿留多人大家也很惧怕依古西奥拉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.62,0:19:39.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们可不会在意这些
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.47,0:19:41.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想好将来做什么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.38,0:19:44.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在在联邦警察研修所学习
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.42,0:19:45.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,联邦警察？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.66,0:19:46.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这可真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.04,0:19:50.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,作为警察立功的话  市民权也不是梦想了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.56,0:20:01.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪  你觉得依古西奥拉的力量是为何而存在的？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.55,0:20:05.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…为帮助朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.25,0:20:10.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  可是…不可以沉溺于这份力量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.59,0:20:17.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且你…必须找到你作为依古西奥拉而存在的意义
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.75,0:20:21.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,存在于这个世界上的人必然有其职责
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.28,0:20:25.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不管是我 还是你 甚至那塔鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.74,0:20:27.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是那并不是命运
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.18,0:20:30.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是要靠自己找到的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.52,0:20:34.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,未来能够靠自己的手来开创
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.72,0:20:36.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,未来…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.24,0:20:39.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,珍惜自己
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.15,0:20:42.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这也是为了未来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.75,0:20:44.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.21,0:20:53.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,塔斯克先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.87,0:20:57.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.65,0:21:00.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对你说了奇怪的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.08,0:21:02.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没事  我很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.64,0:21:05.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那再见
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.79,0:21:06.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.94,0:21:11.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.94,0:21:11.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.04,0:21:18.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  我还能再来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.48,0:21:19.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我很喜欢这里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.95,0:21:22.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不管是那塔鲁的小镇还是塔斯克先生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.43,0:21:24.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那些醉酒的叔叔们也是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.74,0:21:26.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好  随时欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.11,0:21:27.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.72,0:21:30.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那  再见
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.80,0:23:13.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是巴迪·希冯·阿鲁提拉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.65,0:23:19.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我的记忆…在我的幼年时代旅行的功
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.41,0:23:23.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,终于经历到中心塔恐怖袭击了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.23,0:23:27.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在那里有被成为「狂战士」的破坏兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.47,0:23:31.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也被卷进了那场战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.29,0:23:34.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为了救我  白奥林她…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.31,0:23:38.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,白奥林 我到现在也还…
